refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public mysql_xdevapi\TableSelectmysql_xdevapi\Table::select mixedcolumns mixed...
Fetches data from a table.

  &reftitle.returnvalues;


	A TableSelect object; use the execute() method to execute the
  select and return a RowResult object.

  &reftitle.examples;

   mysql_xdevapi\Table::count example


<?php
$session = mysql_xdevapi\getSession("mysqlx://user:password@localhost");

$session->sql("DROP DATABASE IF EXISTS addressbook")->execute();
$session->sql("CREATE DATABASE addressbook")->execute();
$session->sql("CREATE TABLE addressbook.names(name text, age int)")->execute();
$session->sql("INSERT INTO addressbook.names values ('John', 42), ('Sam', 33)")->execute();

$schema = $session->getSchema("addressbook");
$table  = $schema->getTable("names");

$row = $table->select('name', 'age')->execute()->fetchAll();

print_r($row);


   &example.outputs.similar;


Array
(
    [0] => Array
        (
            [name] => John
            [age] => 42
        )
    [1] => Array
        (
            [name] => Sam
            [age] => 33
        )
)
